OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sat 11 Apr to Mon 20 AprFIt
OL,6,Fwill likely remain rather changeable
OL,7,Fduring the first part of this period
OL,8,Fwith showers or occasional longer
OL,9,Fspells of rain affecting many areas.
OL,10,FWhether this takes the form of
OL,11,Fsuccessive weather systems pushing in
OL,12,Ffrom the Atlantic or a more slowly
OL,13,Fevolving weather pattern is rather
OL,14,Fmore unclear. Some drier, brighter
OL,15,Finterludes will also occur and when
OL,16,Fwinds are light, it should feel quite
OL,17,Fwarm, despite temperatures most likely
OL,18,Fbeing close to normal for most. Beyond
OL,19,Fmid-month, high pressure may become
OL,20,Frather more dominant, bringing more in
OL,21,Fthe way of drier and perhaps warmer
OL,22,Fweather, though this will be
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fdetermined by the location and
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Fproximity of where any high is
OL,25,Fpositioned relative to the UK.
FL,164,160,301,260,100,100
PN,16303
SC,0003
CT,20,T
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1775484661
