OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tue 21 Apr to Tue 5 May
OL,6,FHigh pressure will probably be the
OL,7,Fmost dominant pattern during this
OL,8,Fperiod with a good deal of dry weather
OL,9,Facross the UK as whole. Some unsettled
OL,10,Finterludes could develop at times, but
OL,11,Foverall rainfall amounts are expected
OL,12,Fto be below average. Temperatures will
OL,13,Fprobably be near to or slightly above
OL,14,Fnormal, although some cold nights are
OL,15,Fstill possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
